title: BLOCK 16
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. While NYCG stands for New York Chicken and Gyro and may be off-putting to vegetarians and vegans, this place offers street food inspired lunches that includes vegan sandwiches, a monthly vegan special, vegan philly, vegan schnitzel, salads, housemade seitan, vegan slaw, hummus, fries and onion rings fries (separate fryer from meat). Has vegan cheese and mayo. Previously named NYCG.
